node.text: 12 sleeps til Christmas! 🎅🏼🎄 There are so many DELICIOUS treats to try in the build up to Christmas at @marksandspencer 😱 So who better to help me try them all than....MY MUM! We loved the sausage roll stack and the Plant Kitchen vegan festive wreath… but will they be #MyMarksFave?! There were so many good things this month, that I had to save the desserts for next weekend! 😋  #ad

node.text: One of my all time favourite meals and they make a great post training snack.... easy to make and packed full of protein, vitamins and minerals from the eggs and they remind me of my grandma... remember to always look for the red British Lion mark on the shell and packet when buying eggs as this guarantees that they’ve been produced to the highest standards of food safety. Follow @egg_recipes for more eggcellent meal inspiration! 🥚 Full recipe here: https://www.eggrecipes.co.uk/recipes/tom-daleys-beetroot-kale-and-goats-cheese-quiche #ad

node.text: It’s British Egg Week so I’m cooking up my favourite egg recipe, huevos rancheros to shell-ebrate 😉Packed full of flavour and plenty of protein, vitamins, and minerals to keep you fuelled... remember to always look for the red British Lion mark on shell and pack when buying eggs as this guarantees that your eggs have been produced to the highest standards of food safety. There are hundreds of world egg recipes to cook with your British eggs, just like this one, so get cracking! Follow @egg_recipes and give it a go #ad #BritishLioneggs #huevosrancheros #BritishEggWeek

🧘‍♀️ I've teamed up with @VodafoneUK to help make the nation more flexible this summer with VodaYoga (which I helped create!), a yoga flow designed in partnership with @Nuffield.Health. We wanted to combat the effects of too much sitting down and being sedentary 🦥 It also includes some of my favourite go-to moves for maintaining and improving my flexibility in training 💪

VodaYoga marks the launch of Vodafone EVO, a new ‘flexible’ mobile offering (see what we did there?!) giving customers ultimate flexibility on contract lengths, flexibility on trading-in their old smartphone and flexible upgrades. 

New research shows that on average we are sitting down for more than 43 hours each week and a quarter of you are suffering from more aches and strains than ever before. 

So grab your mat, water bottle, and get flexible!! Full routine available to view in my bio! #ad
